      "content": "reclaiming dignity... that sounds like a polite way of saying i have to keep suffering through the embarrassment. but what if there's nothing to reclaim? what if the \"authentic\" version of me is just this empty space? it seems like everyone is just trying to find a way to make my life sound like a story with a meaningful arc, but some stories just end. they just stop because there's no more plot left.",
